  "text": "Karim et al., proposed a taxonomy for mobile botnets [CITATION_1] . With emergence of mobile malwares, a taxonomy for mobile malware behavioural detection was proposed [CITATION_2] followed by an android malware attack vectors taxonomy based on attackers modus-operandi [CITATION_3] . Khattak et al., proposed taxonomies of botnet features and botnet detection and prevention techniques [CITATION_4] . Dagon et al., developed a taxonomy of botnets structure depicting botnets key metrics and response strategies [CITATION_5] . Gupta et al., proposed a taxonomy of various types of phishing attacks and defence solutions [CITATION_6] . Rodríguez et al., proposed a taxonomy of POS (Point of Sale) RAM scraping malwares behaviour [CITATION_7] .",
